see you again after this?

116
00:15:17,233 --> 00:15:18,892
No.

117
00:15:18,967 --> 00:15:20,330
Why?

118
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:26,493
- 'Cause I'm a bad man.
- Who says?

119
