for the school magazine cover.

132
00:16:14,833 --> 00:16:16,799
- You know what I did?
- What did you do?

133
00:16:16,866 --> 00:16:20,889
Go on, just tell him.
Don't be playing no guessing games.

134
00:16:20,967 --> 00:16:22,432
