137
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:31,929
The theme was solitude.

138
00:16:33,933 --> 00:16:37,626
Way to go, Ty. Way to go.
Put it there, boy.

139
00:16:39,033 --> 00:16:40,760
Not too bad.

140
00:16:50,232 --> 00:16:52,255
