178
00:19:38,733 --> 00:19:39,756
Hank: Tommy?

179
00:19:39,833 --> 00:19:43,890
Tommy: He likes to draw.
It calms him down.

180
00:19:43,967 --> 00:19:45,330
Draw?

181
00:19:45,399 --> 00:19:46,922
- Yeah.
- Okay.

182
00:19:46,999 --> 00:19:50,659
