and tell him that I tried.

212
00:21:44,433 --> 00:21:45,797
I don't think so.

213
00:21:46,966 --> 00:21:47,989
Sonny: Okay.

214
00:21:51,132 --> 00:21:53,792
- Open 1 3.
- (buzz)

215
00:22:06,232 --> 00:22:08,698
